#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/editing/introduction.rst:52
msgid ""
"The first controls (X, Y, Z) show the coordinates of the selected point or "
"handle (vertex). In case of a NURBS curve, there is a fourth component "
"available (W), which defines the weight of the selected control point or the "
"median weight."
